{
  "meta": {
    "title": "人的一生",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "estimatedMinutes": [3, 5],
    "start": { "stageId": "birth", "sceneId": "birth_hello" },
    "rngSeedDefault": "life-demo"
  },
  "initial": {
    "stats": {
      "stress": 12,
      "healthDebt": 0,
      "support": 58,
      "wealth": 28,
      "career": 12,
      "luck": 52
    },
    "flags": {},
    "tags": []
  },
  "stages": [
    {
      "id": "birth",
      "title": "诞生",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "birth_hello",
          "narrative": [
            "第一声啼哭落下，世界把光与噪声一并塞给你。",
            "有人在笑，有人在累；名字被轻声念出，像一枚尚未盖章的印章。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "birth_next",
              "label": "时间开始向前流动",
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "childhood", "sceneId": "child_play" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "childhood",
      "title": "幼年",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "child_play",
          "narrative": [
            "你学会把积木搭高，再看着它倒塌。",
            "大人说「要乖」；你只知道风从窗缝里进来时，窗帘像一片慢吞吞的海。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "child_next",
              "label": "进入学龄前记忆",
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "support", "value": 3 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "primary", "sceneId": "pri_school" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "primary",
      "title": "小学",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "pri_school",
          "narrative": [
            "红领巾、课间操、橡皮屑。成绩像一串忽上忽下的台阶。",
            "你开始理解「别人家的孩子」不是一种生物，而是一种天气。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "pri_steady",
              "label": "按部就班，把基础打牢",
              "effects": [
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 6 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 4 }
              ],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "youth", "sceneId": "youth_gate" }
            },
            {
              "id": "pri_wide",
              "label": "多试试兴趣，少盯分数",
              "effects": [
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "support", "value": 8 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 3 }
              ],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "youth", "sceneId": "youth_gate" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "youth",
      "title": "初中与高中",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "youth_gate",
          "narrative": [
            "青春期像一场漫长的耳鸣：友谊、成绩、暗恋与自我怀疑同时放大。",
            "走廊里有人背书，有人在哭；你把心事折成纸飞机，却不敢真的扔出去。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "youth_next",
              "label": "来到高三",
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 10 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "high_pressure", "sceneId": "high_night" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "high_pressure",
      "title": "高三",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "high_night",
          "narrative": [
            "倒计时牌翻得比日历还快。试卷、排名、父母的沉默与期待叠成一张薄被。",
            "深夜台灯下，你反复权衡：再刷一套，还是让身体先投降？"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "grind_late",
              "label": "再熬一小时，把错题啃完",
              "effects": [
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 10 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 12 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "healthDebt", "value": 8 },
                { "op": "addTag", "tag": "熬夜" }
              ],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "gaokao", "sceneId": "gk_before" }
            },
            {
              "id": "rest_ok",
              "label": "准时睡，相信白天的效率",
              "effects": [
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 5 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": -5 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "support", "value": 4 }
              ],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "gaokao", "sceneId": "gk_before" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "gaokao",
      "title": "高考",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "gk_before",
          "narrative": [
            "考场铃声像某种宗教仪式。你摸着准考证的塑封边，突然想起小学那块橡皮。",
            "努力会把概率推到你这边，但人生仍保留「发挥」这个词的余地。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "gk_enter",
              "label": "走进考场，完成这场检定",
              "check": {
                "kind": "threshold",
                "id": "gaokao",
                "label": "高考发挥",
                "modifiers": {
                  "addStatWeights": [{ "stat": "career", "weight": 0.32 }],
                  "luckWeight": 0.12,
                  "stressPenalty": 0.22
                },
                "bands": [
                  {
                    "min": 0,
                    "max": 28,
                    "label": "失常",
                    "next": { "kind": "scene", "sceneId": "gk_result_low" },
                    "effects": [
                      { "op": "setFlag", "key": "tier", "value": false },
                      { "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 18 }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "min": 29,
                    "max": 72,
                    "label": "正常发挥",
                    "next": { "kind": "scene", "sceneId": "gk_result_mid" },
                    "effects": [{ "op": "setFlag", "key": "tier", "value": true }]
                  },
                  {
                    "min": 73,
                    "max": 100,
                    "label": "超常发挥",
                    "next": { "kind": "scene", "sceneId": "gk_result_high" },
                    "effects": [
                      { "op": "setFlag", "key": "tier", "value": true },
                      { "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 12 },
                      { "op": "addStat", "stat": "luck", "value": 6 }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "gk_result_low",
          "narrative": [
            "成绩出来那天，走廊的风有点凉。你看见自己的名次，像被轻轻推了一下腰。",
            "路没有断，只是拐弯更急：你会去一所不曾写进梦里的学校，学会把不甘心磨成耐心。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "from_low",
              "label": "收拾情绪，去下一站",
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 4 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "path_open", "sceneId": "path_campus" }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "gk_result_mid",
          "narrative": [
            "分数与预期大致握手言和。你填志愿时像在拼一张并不完美的地图。",
            "大学城的梧桐树在等你，社团、宿舍与熬夜的论文也在等你。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "from_mid",
              "label": "继续向前",
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 8 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "path_open", "sceneId": "path_campus" }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "gk_result_high",
          "narrative": [
            "榜单上你的名字像意外亮起的灯。你愣住，然后笑出声。",
            "更好的平台并不会替你走路，但它会给你更多选择——以及更多比较。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "from_high",
              "label": "把幸运当成责任",
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 10 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "path_open", "sceneId": "path_campus" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "path_open",
      "title": "大学与起步",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "path_campus",
          "narrative": [
            "图书馆闭馆音乐、实习面试、第一次拿到工资短信。",
            "你开始把「理想」从口号换成可执行清单：房租、存款、父母的电话。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "work_hard",
              "label": "加班换成长，先把路走宽",
              "effects": [
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "wealth", "value": 10 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "career", "value": 10 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 14 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "healthDebt", "value": 10 },
                { "op": "addTag", "tag": "熬夜" }
              ],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "work_life", "sceneId": "work_daily" }
            },
            {
              "id": "work_balance",
              "label": "守住节奏，拒绝无限加班",
              "effects": [
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "support", "value": 8 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": -4 },
                { "op": "addStat", "stat": "wealth", "value": 5 }
              ],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "work_life", "sceneId": "work_daily" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "work_life",
      "title": "职场与家庭",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "work_daily",
          "narrative": [
            "你把「稳定」与「想要」放在天平两端。有人结婚，有人离开城市，有人开始学新技能。",
            "中年不是突然到来的，它是一次次「算了」与「再撑一下」叠出来的。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "to_elder",
              "label": "走向人生的后半程",
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 6 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "elder", "sceneId": "elder_health" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "elder",
      "title": "中老年",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "elder_health",
          "onEnter": [],
          "narrative": [
            "体检报告比天气预报更让你上心。你开始理解「身体」不是背景，而是人生的前台。",
            "早年埋下的习惯，会在多年后以温柔或严厉的方式回来看你。"
          ],
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "elder_ok",
              "label": "这些年还算平稳，学会与自己和解",
              "visibleWhen": { "statMax": { "stat": "healthDebt", "value": 35 } },
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "ending", "sceneId": "end_reflect" }
            },
            {
              "id": "elder_warn",
              "label": "慢性病与药盒成为日常，你仍想抓住体面",
              "visibleWhen": { "statMin": { "stat": "healthDebt", "value": 36 } },
              "effects": [{ "op": "addStat", "stat": "stress", "value": 8 }],
              "next": { "kind": "stage", "stageId": "ending", "sceneId": "end_reflect" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ending",
      "title": "终章",
      "scenes": [
        {
          "id": "end_reflect",
          "isEnding": true,
          "narrative": [
            "故事收束时，你不会带走分数与头衔，只会带走一串被选择雕刻过的日子。",
            "如果再来一次，你会在某个夜晚早点睡吗？还是仍会那样热烈地活？",
            "——人生没有标准答案，只有你愿意如何与遗憾共处。"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
